txt.en: 'I have heard much about what you have done to aid the people here in western Gondor. I think you would make a fine addition to the city guard here in Dol Amroth. Are you interested in joining?'
You have received a summons from Beriaudur, leader of the city guard of Dol Amroth. You should head to the city and make his acquaintance.
You have received a summons asking you to report to Beriaudur in Dol Amroth.
You have received a summons asking you to report to Beriaudur in Dol Amroth.
Beriaudur can be found in Dol Amroth.\n\nBeriaudur, head of the Dol Amroth city guard, is looking forward to speaking with you.
